After deciding to sell their zoo in India and move to Canada, Santosh and Gita Patel board a freighter with their sons and a few remaining animals.
Tragedy strikes when a terrible storm sinks the ship, leaving the Patels' teenage son, Pi (Suraj Sharma), as the only human survivor.Â 
However, Pi is not alone; a fearsome Bengal tiger has also found refuge aboard the lifeboat.
